==Adaptations==
In 2017, a UK theatre production of the poem was developed by Tom Chivers, under the moniker &#x27;Fair Field&#x27;. It included an exhibition at the National Poetry Library and a series of podcasts published by the &quot;Guardian&quot;.

In 2023, Eloise Peniston adapted and directed a Middle English performance of the Trinity B Text at St Edmund Hall. ‘

